    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Avoid adding <code>android.defaults.buildfeatures.buildconfig=true</code> to your <code>gradle.properties</code> file because that property is <a href=\"https://cs.android.com/android-studio/platform/tools/base/+/0bc1c23297760643b03e8cfd8acc52c007a99cd6\" rel=\"noreferrer\">deprecated in AGP 8.0 and is scheduled to be removed in AGP 9.0</a>.</p>\n<p>Instead, add the following to the per-module <code>build.gradle</code> file for each module using <code>BuildConfig</code>:</p>\n<pre><code>android {\n    buildFeatures {\n        buildConfig = true\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
